<chapter><title>Display Widget Classes</title>
<indexterm><primary>Classes</primary>
<secondary>Display Widgets</secondary></indexterm>

<para>Displayable widgets are those that are just used to display object such as images
or text. These objects are not usually interactive and are almost always static in
nature.</para>

